;All the lines with ; at the start are comments and should be left at the top of the file

;zoomlevels a list of zoom values to switch between when using mouse wheel zooming
;font, fontsize - alters the chat text
;xxxheight, xxxwidth - alter various right-hand side panel sizes
;nopassword - change this to true if you want to play without passwords
;showleadersip - change this to false will show number of leaders in a region, rather then leadership values
;dicesorted - change this to true will show combat dice results in sorted order
;language - blank (which is English) or Deutsch currently supported for the program displays
;flashMandatory - mandatory actions 0=flash until next move, -1 = no flash or a number fior the number of flashes required
;flashOptional - optional actions 0=flash until next move, -1 = no flash or a number fior the number of flashes required
;shortGroupDesc - set this to get shorter group descriptions in the chat window
;lastPasswordUsed - a record of the last password you used in case you forget it (I know I have)

